# Ignore everything by default — this git repo is ONLY for the license
# revocation file that ships publicly. The Fiverr folder also contains the
# full Unity project and local client records, which must NEVER be pushed
# here (this repo is PUBLIC — the game itself fetches revoked.txt with no
# authentication).
*

# Explicitly allow only what belongs in the public revocation repo
!.gitignore
!revoked.txt
!README.md

# keys_database.txt (client names/emails) stays LOCAL ONLY — never allowed
# in this list, since this repo is public.
